main event: On March 6, 1964, a flying saucer incident was reported in Roswell, New Mexico, investigated under Project Blue Book.
interesting points: The document is part of the investigations related to the sighting by Project Blue Book., It includes a total of 12 photographs documenting aerial phenomena., The photographs depict unidentified aerial objects against dark backgrounds., The images show bright lights or objects in a night sky with stars visible., Some photographs appear to show round, glowing objects in the sky.
sighted object: unidentified aerial objects (UAO) or unidentified flying objects (UFOs)
